        "created_at": "2022-05-21T08:50:44.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Very reduced to begin with. After working some air into the wine, it breathes up to show notes of musk and meat. It is very much blue fruited and very dense and tight. There is outstanding depth of fruit and a chalky structure. The finish is so strong and expansive and the wine is decades away from its apogee.</p>",
